Same problem happens to me, and I managed to fix it

b. Add an import "from tensorflow.python.ops import gen_image_ops" to import_pb_to_tensorboard.py

diff --git a/tensorflow/python/tools/BUILD b/tensorflow/python/tools/BUILD
index 63f16c5..23e8055 100644

+++ b/tensorflow/python/tools/BUILD
@@ -71,6 +71,7 @@ py_binary(
         "//tensorflow/python:client",
         "//tensorflow/python:framework",
         "//tensorflow/python:framework_ops",
+        "//tensorflow/python:image_ops",
         "//tensorflow/python:platform",
         "//tensorflow/python:summary",
     ],

index 00de044..a83ff1d 100755
--- a/tensorflow/python/tools/import_pb_to_tensorboard.py
+++ b/tensorflow/python/tools/import_pb_to_tensorboard.py
@@ -25,6 +25,7 @@ from tensorflow.core.framework import graph_pb2
 from tensorflow.python.client import session
